@startuml market-data-flow

skinparam nodesep 30
skinparam ranksep 40
skinparam dpi 200
skinparam shadowing false

skinparam {
    BackgroundColor white
    BorderColor #1565C0
    ArrowColor #1565C0
    DefaultFontColor #2C3E50
    
    NoteBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
    NoteBorderColor #1565C0
    
    ComponentBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
    RectangleBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
    DatabaseBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
    QueueBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
    StorageBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
    CloudBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
    
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
    ActorBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
    
    ClassBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
}

title 行情数据流处理流程

actor "第三方行情 API" as api
participant "StockApiClient\n定时拉取" as client
queue "Kafka\nstock-price-updates" as kafka
participant "KafkaConsumer\n消费者" as consumer
database "Redis\n缓存" as redis
database "MySQL\n持久化" as mysql
participant "WebSocket\n推送服务" as websocket
actor "前端用户" as user

== 行情数据拉取 ==
client -> api : 定时拉取行情数据\n(每 3 秒)
api --> client : 返回最新价格

== 数据发布到 Kafka ==
client -> kafka : 发布行情消息\n{stockCode, price, volume...}
note right
  消息格式：
  {
    "stockCode": "600519",
    "price": 1850.00,
    "changeRate": 2.5,
    "volume": 1234567,
    "timestamp": "2026-03-09T10:30:00"
  }
end note

== 消费者处理 ==
kafka -> consumer : 消费行情消息
consumer -> redis : 更新缓存\nKEY: stock:600519\nTTL: 5秒
consumer -> mysql : 批量写入数据库\n(每 10 秒一次)

== 实时推送 ==
consumer -> websocket : 通知有新数据
websocket -> user : WebSocket 推送\n实时更新价格

note over redis
  缓存结构：
  - stock:{code} -> 最新价格
  - stock:{code}:kline:day -> 日K线数据
  - stock:{code}:indicators -> 技术指标
end note

@enduml
